data.description: Meticulously maintained brick rancher in Laurel Bend, a desirable neighborhood with convenient access to shopping, dining and entertainment. This home features a spacious primary suite with double trey ceiling, a spa-like bathroom with dual sinks, a garden tub and separate shower, and large walk-in closet. The kitchen is a chef’s dream with granite countertops, custom cabinets, and an eat-in breakfast nook. The family room is adjacent to the kitchen and has gorgeous hardwood floors and a cozy fireplace for those chilly nights. The fenced backyard has a covered patio and established garden. Lennox PureAir HVAC system 2023; Roof 2019; Whole house surge protection 2022; Storm Shelte
